data.description: Priced for Immediate Sale! This move-in ready 4 bdrm, 3 ba, 2,539 sq ft S Salem home presents an exciting opportunity for buyers thanks to a recent price drop & motivated sellers. Multiple primary suites, plenty of room for toys & upgrades in 2020 including roof, furnace, AC & WH, this 1990s single-level property has ample space to spread out & modern amenities. A desirable neighborhood & abundant living space make this a smart purchase for the right buyer to act quickly before the winter slowdown.
